@code{function (f_1, f_2, ...)} as an argument; here @code{f_1}, @code{f_2},
@dots{} are the names of functions.  For example the expression,

@example
mode_declare ([function (f_1, f_2, ...)], fixnum)
@end example

declares that the values returned by @code{f_1}, @code{f_2}, @dots{} are
single-word integers.

